ids":[10751,16,18,12],"popularity":18.8917,"vote_count":19405,"poster_path":"/sKCr78MXSLixwmZ8DyJLrpMsd15.jpg","release_date":"1994-06-15","vote_average":8.252,"backdrop_path":"/6GF9uJs7AnbcJvyfoZyjZv063Oo.jpg","original_title":"The Lion King","original_language":"en"},{"id":661996,"adult":false,"title":"Un Hombre Violento","video":false,"overview":"Bent on avenging the death of his gambling addicted father, Julian Carrera embarks on a violent spree with deadly consequences.","genre_ids":[28,80,18,53],"popularity":0.1719,"vote_count":5,"poster_path":"/wOw0EtETlLyqcDG1Xq3GtaZWj3F.jpg","release_date":"1984-01-01","vote_average":4.2,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Un Hombre Violento","original_language":"es"},{"id":8856,"adult":false,"title":"The Karate Kid Part II","video":false,"overview":"Summoned by his dying father, Miyagi returns to his homeland of Okinawa, with Daniel, after a 40-year exile. There he must confront Yukie, the love of his youth, and Sato, his former best friend turned vengeful rival. Sato is bent on a fight to the death, even if it means the destruction of their village. Daniel finds his own love in Yukia's niece, Kumiko, and his own enemy in Sato's nephew, the vicious Chozen. Now, far away from the tournaments, cheering crowds and safety of home, Daniel will face his greatest challenge ever when the cost of honor is life itself.","genre_ids":[12,18,28,10749,10751],"popularity":3.4369,"vote_count":2415,"poster_path":"/k0OwgRR6PNu7h3SiqpCbRdZWNaG.jpg","release_date":"1986-06-18","vote_average":6.335,"backdrop_path":"/7rfcRXbFD0xr8NteNq1hwXUd4Af.jpg","original_title":"The Karate Kid Part II","original_language":"en"},{"id":8860,"adult":false,"title":"Metro","video":false,"overview":"Roper, a hostage negotiator catches a murderous bank robber after a blown heist. The bank robber escapes and immediately goes after the man who put him behind bars.","genre_ids":[28,35,80],"popularity":1.0872,"vote_count":601,"poster_path":"/nvfyHYv1EDpYai5pCGqBeRf3tax.jpg","release_date":"1997-01-16","vote_average":5.704,"backdrop_path":"/vGzPiKNj3Tw9NR4F6EyexqniEqm.jpg","original_title":"Metro","original_language":"en"},{"id":8867,"adult":false,"title":"The Punisher","video":false,"overview":"The avenging angel of Marvel Comics fame comes brilliantly to life in this searing action-adventure thriller! Dolph Lundgren stars as Frank Castle, a veteran cop who loses his entire family to a mafia car bomb. His ex-partner believes Castle survived the blast and became the Punisher, living in the sewers and exacting vigilante violence against mob bosses throughout the city. When the populace is caught in the midst of a gang war that he caused, Castle must again emerge from the shadows and save the innocent.","genre_ids":[28,80,18,53],"popularity":1.8603,"vote_count":653,"poster_path":"/tA0O0hYyHX7Hl2Fl8VEtGtfBtjI.jpg","release_date":"1989-10-05","vote_average":5.768,"backdrop_path":"/tFmrdnfXM0p6ihMTFpptYOKEfSl.jpg","original_title":"The Punisher","original_language":"en"},{"id":8741,"adult":false,"title":"The Thin Red Line","video":false,"overview":"The story of a group of men, an Army Rifle company called C-for-Charlie, who change, suffer, and ultimately make essential discoveries about themselves during the fierce World War II battle of Guadalcanal. It follows their journey, from the surprise of an unopposed landing, through the bloody and exhausting battles that follow, to the ultimate departure of those who survived.","genre_ids":[18,36,10752],"popularity":4.1493,"vote_count":3221,"poster_path":"/seMydAaoxQP6F0xbE1jOcTmn5Jr.jpg","release_date":"1998-12-23","vote_average":7.445,"backdrop_path":"/hsDyfAk2ml82IrpPC4AHvxvuTsn.jpg","original_title":"The Thin Red Line","original_language":"en"},{"id":8840,"adult":false,"title":"DragonHeart","video":false,"overview":"In an ancient time when majestic fire-breathers soared through the skies, a knight named Bowen comes face to face and heart to heart with the last dragon on Earth, Draco. Taking up arms to suppress a tyrant king, Bowen soon realizes his task will be harder than he'd imagined: If he kills the king, Draco will die as well.","genre_ids":[14,28,12,18],"popularity":4.3924,"vote_count":2106,"poster_path":"/1J2FvxEoEKMFT9TjUdfhm0MJhZD.jpg","release_date":"1996-05-31","vote_average":6.545,"backdrop_path":"/xbqluNfftDJtxDsqcpx9kKme4LF.jpg","original_title":"DragonHeart","original_language":"en"},{"id":8842,"adult":false,"title":"Against the Ropes","video":false,"overview":"A fictional story inspired by North America's most famous female boxing promoter, Jackie Kallen. Her struggle to survive and succeed in a male dominated sport.","genre_ids":[10749,18],"popularity":0.602,"vote_count":129,"poster_path":"/9CuODYTA3vvrGluaIl0hMPsEIK8.jpg","release_date":"2004-02-20","vote_average":5.043,"backdrop_path":"/i9AIrb3C7l3wuxuqYbrv4rBCEHp.jpg","original_title":"Against the Ropes","original_language":"en"},{"id":8456,"adult":false,"title":"Never Back Down","video":false,"overview":"Jake, full of anger after his father's death, is just starting to find a place for himself at his new Orlando high school - until Ryan, head of an underground MMA fight club, picks Jake out as a prime opponent. After being trounced by Ryan in front of the entire school, Jake begins training under the firm, moral guidance of a MMA master, where he learns how to fight... and how to avoid a fight. But it becomes obvious that a rematch will be inevitable if Jake wants to stop Ryan and his bullying, once and for all.","genre_ids":[18,28],"popularity":4.968,"vote_count":2442,"poster_path":"/8oRUTyP1QAtGDMvRpKZyuyFPG0U.jpg","release_date":"2008-03-04","vote_average":6.8,"backdrop_path":"/h71xyiurUscD6uIPbECyso1Lwb9.jpg","original_title":"Never Back Down","original_language":"en"},{"id":8555,"adult":false,"title":"Creep","video":false,"overview":"Trapped in a London subway station, a woman who's being pursued by a potential attacker heads into the unknown labyrinth of tunnels benea